      "score": 0.042222569982478746,
      "text": "14 September 2004 Baghdad bombing\nThe 14 September 2004 Baghdad bombing was a suicide car bomb attack on a market, near a police headquarters, in Baghdad, the capital city of Iraq, on 14 September 2004, killing 47 people and wounding 114.",
