        "node_id": "chunk:kamryn_belle_0",
        "score": 0.002061980888840182,
        "text": "Kamryn Belle\nFor the most part she was raised in the Netherlands, where she currently lives. Kamryn is the youngest of six children and comes from a musical family. Her dad was a singer in a band and her three brothers all played an instrument. When she was growing up Kamryn started singing more often and gained more experience. She now writes and records songs in her home studio.",
        "metadata": {
