        "score": 0.04223816084796873,
        "text": "Northeast blackout of 2003\nThe Northeast blackout of 2003 was a widespread power outage throughout parts of the Northeastern and Midwestern United States and the Canadian province of Ontario on Thursday, August 14, 2003, just after 4: 10 p.m. EDT.",
