      "title": "Dave Sharp",
      "score": 0.04170142654790463,
      "text": "Dave Sharp\nDave Sharp (born 28 January 1959) is an English guitarist who co-founded, along with Mike Peters, the Welsh punk/new wave band The Alarm.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05002825531347086,
        "graph": 0.047286287084985515,
